---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Biografi
pageId: biografi
permalink: /biografi/index.html
---

<section class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950/40 p-6">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-6">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Biografi</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">Långscroll. Ankare: <span class="font-mono">#p-001</span> … <span class="font-mono">#p-276</span>.</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-500">Tips: du kan också gå till <span class="font-mono">/biografi/12</span> eller <span class="font-mono">/biografi/page/12</span> (redirect).</p>
    </div>

    <form class="flex items-center gap-2" data-jump-form>
      <label class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-400" for="page">Hoppa</label>
      <input class="w-24 rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 bg-black/40 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-zinc-600" id="page" name="page" type="number" min="1" max="276" placeholder="t.ex. 12" />
      <button class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 px-3 py-2 text-sm hover:border-zinc-600" type="submit">Gå</button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <details class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-black/30 p-4">
    <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none text-sm text-zinc-200">Innehåll (TOC)</summary>
    <div class="mt-4 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
      {% for p in biografi.pages | slice(0, 20) %}
        <a class="no-underline" href="#{{ p.id }}">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono text-zinc-300 hover:border-zinc-600">
            {{ p.id }} <span class="text-zinc-500">— page {{ p.page }}</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="mt-3 text-xs text-zinc-500">MVP visar första 20 sidor i TOC. Ankare finns för alla 276.</div>
  </details>
</section>

<div class="mt-8 grid gap-5">
  {% biografiPages biografi.pages %}
</div>
